              FROM 
              (
                  SELECT TOP(1) s.id, s.cinemahall_id, s.cost, s.film_id, s.seancedate, f.id AS id0, f.datefinish, f.datestart, f.description, f.duration, f.genre_id, f.title, f.poster, f.restriction, g.id AS id1, g.description AS description0, g.title AS title0, c.hallnumber, c.hallname
                  FROM seance AS s
                  INNER JOIN film AS f ON s.film_id == f.id
                  INNER JOIN genre AS g ON f.genre_id == g.id
                  INNER JOIN cinemahall AS c ON s.cinemahall_id == c.hallnumber
                  WHERE s.id == @__id_0
              ) AS t
              LEFT JOIN 
              (
                  SELECT h.id, h.cinemahall_id, h.row_number, h0.id AS id0, h0.hallrow_id, h0.seat_number
                  FROM hallrow AS h
                  LEFT JOIN hallseat AS h0 ON h.id == h0.hallrow_id
              ) AS t0 ON t.hallnumber == t0.cinemahall_id
              LEFT JOIN 
              (
                  SELECT s0.ReservedSeancesID, s0.ReservedSeatsID, h1.id, h1.hallrow_id, h1.seat_number
                  FROM SeanceReservedSeats AS s0
                  INNER JOIN hallseat AS h1 ON s0.ReservedSeatsID == h1.id
              ) AS t1 ON t.id == t1.ReservedSeancesID
              LEFT JOIN 
              (
                  SELECT s1.BoughtSeancesID, s1.BoughtSeatsID, h2.id, h2.hallrow_id, h2.seat_number
                  FROM SeanceBoughtSeats AS s1
                  INNER JOIN hallseat AS h2 ON s1.BoughtSeatsID == h2.id
              ) AS t2 ON t.id == t2.BoughtSeancesID
              ORDER BY t.id ASC, t.id0 ASC, t.id1 ASC, t.hallnumber ASC, t0.id ASC, t0.id0 ASC, t1.ReservedSeancesID ASC, t1.ReservedSeatsID ASC, t1.id ASC, t2.BoughtSeancesID ASC, t2.BoughtSeatsID ASC),

          False, 
          False, 
          True
      )
          .SingleOrDefault()'

          SELECT s.id, s.cinemahall_id, s.cost, s.film_id, s.seancedate, f.id AS id0, f.datefinish, f.datestart, f.description, f.duration, f.genre_id, f.title, f.poster, f.restriction, g.id AS id1, g.description AS description0, g.title AS title0, c.hallnumber, c.hallname

          INNER JOIN genre AS g ON f.genre_id = g.id
          INNER JOIN cinemahall AS c ON s.cinemahall_id = c.hallnumber
          WHERE s.id = @__id_0
          LIMIT 1
      ) AS t
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT h.id, h.cinemahall_id, h.row_number, h0.id AS id0, h0.hallrow_id, h0.seat_number
          FROM hallrow AS h

              SELECT t.id, t.cinemahall_id, t.cost, t.film_id, t.seancedate, t.id0, t.datefinish, t.datestart, t.description, t.duration, t.genre_id, t.title, t.poster, t.restriction, t.id1, t.description0, t.title0, t.hallnumber, t.hallname, t0.id, t0.cinemahall_id, t0.row_number, t0.id0, t0.hallrow_id, t0.seat_number, t1.ReservedSeancesID, t1.ReservedSeatsID, t1.id, t1.hallrow_id, t1.seat_number, t2.BoughtSeancesID, t2.BoughtSeatsID, t2.id, t2.hallrow_id, t2.seat_number
              FROM 
              (
                  SELECT TOP(1) s.id, s.cinemahall_id, s.cost, s.film_id, s.seancedate, f.id AS id0, f.datefinish, f.datestart, f.description, f.duration, f.genre_id, f.title, f.poster, f.restriction, g.id AS id1, g.description AS description0, g.title AS title0, c.hallnumber, c.hallname
                  FROM seance AS s
                  INNER JOIN film AS f ON s.film_id == f.id
                  INNER JOIN genre AS g ON f.genre_id == g.id
                  INNER JOIN cinemahall AS c ON s.cinemahall_id == c.hallnumber
                  WHERE s.id == @__id_0
              ) AS t
              LEFT JOIN 
              (
                  SELECT h.id, h.cinemahall_id, h.row_number, h0.id AS id0, h0.hallrow_id, h0.seat_number
                  FROM hallrow AS h
                  LEFT JOIN hallseat AS h0 ON h.id == h0.hallrow_id
              ) AS t0 ON t.hallnumber == t0.cinemahall_id
              LEFT JOIN 
              (
                  SELECT s0.ReservedSeancesID, s0.ReservedSeatsID, h1.id, h1.hallrow_id, h1.seat_number
                  FROM SeanceReservedSeats AS s0
                  INNER JOIN hallseat AS h1 ON s0.ReservedSeatsID == h1.id
              ) AS t1 ON t.id == t1.ReservedSeancesID
              LEFT JOIN 
              (
                  SELECT s1.BoughtSeancesID, s1.BoughtSeatsID, h2.id, h2.hallrow_id, h2.seat_number
                  FROM SeanceBoughtSeats AS s1
                  INNER JOIN hallseat AS h2 ON s1.BoughtSeatsID == h2.id
              ) AS t2 ON t.id == t2.BoughtSeancesID
              ORDER BY t.id ASC, t.id0 ASC, t.id1 ASC, t.hallnumber ASC, t0.id ASC, t0.id0 ASC, t1.ReservedSeancesID ASC, t1.ReservedSeatsID ASC, t1.id ASC, t2.BoughtSeancesID ASC, t2.BoughtSeatsID ASC),

          CinemaLibrary.ApplicationContext, 
          False, 
          False, 
          True
      )
          .SingleOrDefault()'

      SELECT t.id, t.cinemahall_id, t.cost, t.film_id, t.seancedate, t.id0, t.datefinish, t.datestart, t.description, t.duration, t.genre_id, t.title, t.poster, t.restriction, t.id1, t.description0, t.title0, t.hallnumber, t.hallname, t0.id, t0.cinemahall_id, t0.row_number, t0.id0, t0.hallrow_id, t0.seat_number, t1."ReservedSeancesID", t1."ReservedSeatsID", t1.id, t1.hallrow_id, t1.seat_number, t2."BoughtSeancesID", t2."BoughtSeatsID", t2.id, t2.hallrow_id, t2.seat_number
      FROM (
          SELECT s.id, s.cinemahall_id, s.cost, s.film_id, s.seancedate, f.id AS id0, f.datefinish, f.datestart, f.description, f.duration, f.genre_id, f.title, f.poster, f.restriction, g.id AS id1, g.description AS description0, g.title AS title0, c.hallnumber, c.hallname
          FROM seance AS s
          INNER JOIN film AS f ON s.film_id = f.id
          INNER JOIN genre AS g ON f.genre_id = g.id
          INNER JOIN cinemahall AS c ON s.cinemahall_id = c.hallnumber
          WHERE s.id = @__id_0
          LIMIT 1
      ) AS t
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT h.id, h.cinemahall_id, h.row_number, h0.id AS id0, h0.hallrow_id, h0.seat_number
          FROM hallrow AS h
          LEFT JOIN hallseat AS h0 ON h.id = h0.hallrow_id
      ) AS t0 ON t.hallnumber = t0.cinemahall_id
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT s0."ReservedSeancesID", s0."ReservedSeatsID", h1.id, h1.hallrow_id, h1.seat_number
          FROM "SeanceReservedSeats" AS s0
          INNER JOIN hallseat AS h1 ON s0."ReservedSeatsID" = h1.id
      ) AS t1 ON t.id = t1."ReservedSeancesID"
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT s1."BoughtSeancesID", s1."BoughtSeatsID", h2.id, h2.hallrow_id, h2.seat_number
          FROM "SeanceBoughtSeats" AS s1
          INNER JOIN hallseat AS h2 ON s1."BoughtSeatsID" = h2.id
      ) AS t2 ON t.id = t2."BoughtSeancesID"
      ORDER BY t.id, t.id0, t.id1, t.hallnumber, t0.id, t0.id0, t1."ReservedSeancesID", t1."ReservedSeatsID", t1.id, t2."BoughtSeancesID", t2."BoughtSeatsID"

      Opened connection to database 'cinema' on server 'tcp://localhost:5432'.
dbug: 24.06.2022 10:54:26.794 RelationalEventId.CommandExecuting[20100] (Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command) 
      Executing DbCommand [Parameters=[@__id_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
      SELECT t.id, t.cinemahall_id, t.cost, t.film_id, t.seancedate, t.id0, t.datefinish, t.datestart, t.description, t.duration, t.genre_id, t.title, t.poster, t.restriction, t.id1, t.description0, t.title0, t.hallnumber, t.hallname, t0.id, t0.cinemahall_id, t0.row_number, t0.id0, t0.hallrow_id, t0.seat_number, t1."ReservedSeancesID", t1."ReservedSeatsID", t1.id, t1.hallrow_id, t1.seat_number, t2."BoughtSeancesID", t2."BoughtSeatsID", t2.id, t2.hallrow_id, t2.seat_number
      FROM (
          SELECT s.id, s.cinemahall_id, s.cost, s.film_id, s.seancedate, f.id AS id0, f.datefinish, f.datestart, f.description, f.duration, f.genre_id, f.title, f.poster, f.restriction, g.id AS id1, g.description AS description0, g.title AS title0, c.hallnumber, c.hallname
          FROM seance AS s
          INNER JOIN film AS f ON s.film_id = f.id
          INNER JOIN genre AS g ON f.genre_id = g.id
          INNER JOIN cinemahall AS c ON s.cinemahall_id = c.hallnumber
          WHERE s.id = @__id_0
          LIMIT 1
      ) AS t
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT h.id, h.cinemahall_id, h.row_number, h0.id AS id0, h0.hallrow_id, h0.seat_number
          FROM hallrow AS h
          LEFT JOIN hallseat AS h0 ON h.id = h0.hallrow_id
      ) AS t0 ON t.hallnumber = t0.cinemahall_id
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT s0."ReservedSeancesID", s0."ReservedSeatsID", h1.id, h1.hallrow_id, h1.seat_number
          FROM "SeanceReservedSeats" AS s0
          INNER JOIN hallseat AS h1 ON s0."ReservedSeatsID" = h1.id
      ) AS t1 ON t.id = t1."ReservedSeancesID"
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT s1."BoughtSeancesID", s1."BoughtSeatsID", h2.id, h2.hallrow_id, h2.seat_number
          FROM "SeanceBoughtSeats" AS s1
          INNER JOIN hallseat AS h2 ON s1."BoughtSeatsID" = h2.id
      ) AS t2 ON t.id = t2."BoughtSeancesID"

      FROM (
          SELECT s.id, s.cinemahall_id, s.cost, s.film_id, s.seancedate, f.id AS id0, f.datefinish, f.datestart, f.description, f.duration, f.genre_id, f.title, f.poster, f.restriction, g.id AS id1, g.description AS description0, g.title AS title0, c.hallnumber, c.hallname
          FROM seance AS s
          INNER JOIN film AS f ON s.film_id = f.id
          INNER JOIN genre AS g ON f.genre_id = g.id
          INNER JOIN cinemahall AS c ON s.cinemahall_id = c.hallnumber
          WHERE s.id = @__id_0
          LIMIT 1
      ) AS t
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT h.id, h.cinemahall_id, h.row_number, h0.id AS id0, h0.hallrow_id, h0.seat_number
          FROM hallrow AS h
          LEFT JOIN hallseat AS h0 ON h.id = h0.hallrow_id
      ) AS t0 ON t.hallnumber = t0.cinemahall_id
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT s0."ReservedSeancesID", s0."ReservedSeatsID", h1.id, h1.hallrow_id, h1.seat_number
          FROM "SeanceReservedSeats" AS s0
          INNER JOIN hallseat AS h1 ON s0."ReservedSeatsID" = h1.id
      ) AS t1 ON t.id = t1."ReservedSeancesID"
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT s1."BoughtSeancesID", s1."BoughtSeatsID", h2.id, h2.hallrow_id, h2.seat_number
          FROM "SeanceBoughtSeats" AS s1
          INNER JOIN hallseat AS h2 ON s1."BoughtSeatsID" = h2.id
      ) AS t2 ON t.id = t2."BoughtSeancesID"
      ORDER BY t.id, t.id0, t.id1, t.hallnumber, t0.id, t0.id0, t1."ReservedSeancesID", t1."ReservedSeatsID", t1.id, t2."BoughtSeancesID", t2."BoughtSeatsID"

      INNER JOIN genre AS g ON f.genre_id = g.id
      INNER JOIN cinemahall AS c ON s.cinemahall_id = c.hallnumber

          FROM hallrow AS h
          LEFT JOIN hallseat AS h0 ON h.id = h0.hallrow_id
      ) AS t ON c.hallnumber = t.cinemahall_id
      WHERE f.id = @__id_0
      ORDER BY s.id, f.id, g.id, c.hallnumber, t.id

      Executing DbCommand [Parameters=[@__id_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
      SELECT s.id, s.cinemahall_id, s.cost, s.film_id, s.seancedate, f.id, f.datefinish, f.datestart, f.description, f.duration, f.genre_id, f.title, f.poster, f.restriction, g.id, g.description, g.title, c.hallnumber, c.hallname, t.id, t.cinemahall_id, t.row_number, t.id0, t.hallrow_id, t.seat_number
      FROM seance AS s
      INNER JOIN film AS f ON s.film_id = f.id
      INNER JOIN genre AS g ON f.genre_id = g.id
      INNER JOIN cinemahall AS c ON s.cinemahall_id = c.hallnumber
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT h.id, h.cinemahall_id, h.row_number, h0.id AS id0, h0.hallrow_id, h0.seat_number
          FROM hallrow AS h
          LEFT JOIN hallseat AS h0 ON h.id = h0.hallrow_id
      ) AS t ON c.hallnumber = t.cinemahall_id
      WHERE f.id = @__id_0
      ORDER BY s.id, f.id, g.id, c.hallnumber, t.id

      SELECT t.id, t.cinemahall_id, t.cost, t.film_id, t.seancedate, t.id0, t.datefinish, t.datestart, t.description, t.duration, t.genre_id, t.title, t.poster, t.restriction, t.id1, t.description0, t.title0, t.hallnumber, t.hallname, t0.id, t0.cinemahall_id, t0.row_number, t0.id0, t0.hallrow_id, t0.seat_number, t1."ReservedSeancesID", t1."ReservedSeatsID", t1.id, t1.hallrow_id, t1.seat_number, t2."BoughtSeancesID", t2."BoughtSeatsID", t2.id, t2.hallrow_id, t2.seat_number
      FROM (
          SELECT s.id, s.cinemahall_id, s.cost, s.film_id, s.seancedate, f.id AS id0, f.datefinish, f.datestart, f.description, f.duration, f.genre_id, f.title, f.poster, f.restriction, g.id AS id1, g.description AS description0, g.title AS title0, c.hallnumber, c.hallname
          FROM seance AS s
          INNER JOIN film AS f ON s.film_id = f.id
          INNER JOIN genre AS g ON f.genre_id = g.id
          INNER JOIN cinemahall AS c ON s.cinemahall_id = c.hallnumber
          WHERE s.id = @__id_0
          LIMIT 1
      ) AS t
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT h.id, h.cinemahall_id, h.row_number, h0.id AS id0, h0.hallrow_id, h0.seat_number
          FROM hallrow AS h
          LEFT JOIN hallseat AS h0 ON h.id = h0.hallrow_id
      ) AS t0 ON t.hallnumber = t0.cinemahall_id
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT s0."ReservedSeancesID", s0."ReservedSeatsID", h1.id, h1.hallrow_id, h1.seat_number
          FROM "SeanceReservedSeats" AS s0
          INNER JOIN hallseat AS h1 ON s0."ReservedSeatsID" = h1.id
      ) AS t1 ON t.id = t1."ReservedSeancesID"
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT s1."BoughtSeancesID", s1."BoughtSeatsID", h2.id, h2.hallrow_id, h2.seat_number
          FROM "SeanceBoughtSeats" AS s1
          INNER JOIN hallseat AS h2 ON s1."BoughtSeatsID" = h2.id
      ) AS t2 ON t.id = t2."BoughtSeancesID"
      ORDER BY t.id, t.id0, t.id1, t.hallnumber, t0.id, t0.id0, t1."ReservedSeancesID", t1."ReservedSeatsID", t1.id, t2."BoughtSeancesID", t2."BoughtSeatsID"

      Executing DbCommand [Parameters=[@__id_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
      SELECT s.id, s.cinemahall_id, s.cost, s.film_id, s.seancedate, f.id, f.datefinish, f.datestart, f.description, f.duration, f.genre_id, f.title, f.poster, f.restriction, g.id, g.description, g.title, c.hallnumber, c.hallname, t.id, t.cinemahall_id, t.row_number, t.id0, t.hallrow_id, t.seat_number
      FROM seance AS s
      INNER JOIN film AS f ON s.film_id = f.id
      INNER JOIN genre AS g ON f.genre_id = g.id
      INNER JOIN cinemahall AS c ON s.cinemahall_id = c.hallnumber
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT h.id, h.cinemahall_id, h.row_number, h0.id AS id0, h0.hallrow_id, h0.seat_number
          FROM hallrow AS h
          LEFT JOIN hallseat AS h0 ON h.id = h0.hallrow_id
      ) AS t ON c.hallnumber = t.cinemahall_id
      WHERE f.id = @__id_0
      ORDER BY s.id, f.id, g.id, c.hallnumber, t.id

      Executing DbCommand [Parameters=[@__id_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
      SELECT t.id, t.cinemahall_id, t.cost, t.film_id, t.seancedate, t.id0, t.datefinish, t.datestart, t.description, t.duration, t.genre_id, t.title, t.poster, t.restriction, t.id1, t.description0, t.title0, t.hallnumber, t.hallname, t0.id, t0.cinemahall_id, t0.row_number, t0.id0, t0.hallrow_id, t0.seat_number, t1."ReservedSeancesID", t1."ReservedSeatsID", t1.id, t1.hallrow_id, t1.seat_number, t2."BoughtSeancesID", t2."BoughtSeatsID", t2.id, t2.hallrow_id, t2.seat_number
      FROM (
          SELECT s.id, s.cinemahall_id, s.cost, s.film_id, s.seancedate, f.id AS id0, f.datefinish, f.datestart, f.description, f.duration, f.genre_id, f.title, f.poster, f.restriction, g.id AS id1, g.description AS description0, g.title AS title0, c.hallnumber, c.hallname
          FROM seance AS s
          INNER JOIN film AS f ON s.film_id = f.id
          INNER JOIN genre AS g ON f.genre_id = g.id
          INNER JOIN cinemahall AS c ON s.cinemahall_id = c.hallnumber
          WHERE s.id = @__id_0
          LIMIT 1
      ) AS t
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT h.id, h.cinemahall_id, h.row_number, h0.id AS id0, h0.hallrow_id, h0.seat_number
          FROM hallrow AS h
          LEFT JOIN hallseat AS h0 ON h.id = h0.hallrow_id
      ) AS t0 ON t.hallnumber = t0.cinemahall_id
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT s0."ReservedSeancesID", s0."ReservedSeatsID", h1.id, h1.hallrow_id, h1.seat_number
          FROM "SeanceReservedSeats" AS s0
          INNER JOIN hallseat AS h1 ON s0."ReservedSeatsID" = h1.id
      ) AS t1 ON t.id = t1."ReservedSeancesID"
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT s1."BoughtSeancesID", s1."BoughtSeatsID", h2.id, h2.hallrow_id, h2.seat_number
          FROM "SeanceBoughtSeats" AS s1
          INNER JOIN hallseat AS h2 ON s1."BoughtSeatsID" = h2.id
      ) AS t2 ON t.id = t2."BoughtSeancesID"
      ORDER BY t.id, t.id0, t.id1, t.hallnumber, t0.id, t0.id0, t1."ReservedSeancesID", t1."ReservedSeatsID", t1.id, t2."BoughtSeancesID", t2."BoughtSeatsID"

      SELECT s.id, s.cinemahall_id, s.cost, s.film_id, s.seancedate, f.id, f.datefinish, f.datestart, f.description, f.duration, f.genre_id, f.title, f.poster, f.restriction, g.id, g.description, g.title, c.hallnumber, c.hallname, t.id, t.cinemahall_id, t.row_number, t.id0, t.hallrow_id, t.seat_number
      FROM seance AS s
      INNER JOIN film AS f ON s.film_id = f.id
      INNER JOIN genre AS g ON f.genre_id = g.id
      INNER JOIN cinemahall AS c ON s.cinemahall_id = c.hallnumber
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT h.id, h.cinemahall_id, h.row_number, h0.id AS id0, h0.hallrow_id, h0.seat_number
          FROM hallrow AS h
          LEFT JOIN hallseat AS h0 ON h.id = h0.hallrow_id
      ) AS t ON c.hallnumber = t.cinemahall_id
      WHERE f.id = @__id_0
      ORDER BY s.id, f.id, g.id, c.hallnumber, t.id

      SELECT s.id, s.cinemahall_id, s.cost, s.film_id, s.seancedate, f.id, f.datefinish, f.datestart, f.description, f.duration, f.genre_id, f.title, f.poster, f.restriction, g.id, g.description, g.title, c.hallnumber, c.hallname, t.id, t.cinemahall_id, t.row_number, t.id0, t.hallrow_id, t.seat_number

              SELECT t.id, t.cinemahall_id, t.cost, t.film_id, t.seancedate, t.id0, t.datefinish, t.datestart, t.description, t.duration, t.genre_id, t.title, t.poster, t.restriction, t.id1, t.description0, t.title0, t.hallnumber, t.hallname, t0.id, t0.cinemahall_id, t0.row_number, t0.id0, t0.hallrow_id, t0.seat_number, t1.ReservedSeancesID, t1.ReservedSeatsID, t1.id, t1.hallrow_id, t1.seat_number, t2.BoughtSeancesID, t2.BoughtSeatsID, t2.id, t2.hallrow_id, t2.seat_number
              FROM 
              (
                  SELECT TOP(1) s.id, s.cinemahall_id, s.cost, s.film_id, s.seancedate, f.id AS id0, f.datefinish, f.datestart, f.description, f.duration, f.genre_id, f.title, f.poster, f.restriction, g.id AS id1, g.description AS description0, g.title AS title0, c.hallnumber, c.hallname
                  FROM seance AS s
                  INNER JOIN film AS f ON s.film_id == f.id
                  INNER JOIN genre AS g ON f.genre_id == g.id
                  INNER JOIN cinemahall AS c ON s.cinemahall_id == c.hallnumber
                  WHERE s.id == @__id_0
              ) AS t
              LEFT JOIN 
              (
                  SELECT h.id, h.cinemahall_id, h.row_number, h0.id AS id0, h0.hallrow_id, h0.seat_number
                  FROM hallrow AS h
                  LEFT JOIN hallseat AS h0 ON h.id == h0.hallrow_id
              ) AS t0 ON t.hallnumber == t0.cinemahall_id
              LEFT JOIN 
              (
                  SELECT s0.ReservedSeancesID, s0.ReservedSeatsID, h1.id, h1.hallrow_id, h1.seat_number
                  FROM SeanceReservedSeats AS s0
                  INNER JOIN hallseat AS h1 ON s0.ReservedSeatsID == h1.id
              ) AS t1 ON t.id == t1.ReservedSeancesID
              LEFT JOIN 
              (
                  SELECT s1.BoughtSeancesID, s1.BoughtSeatsID, h2.id, h2.hallrow_id, h2.seat_number
                  FROM SeanceBoughtSeats AS s1
                  INNER JOIN hallseat AS h2 ON s1.BoughtSeatsID == h2.id
              ) AS t2 ON t.id == t2.BoughtSeancesID
              ORDER BY t.id ASC, t.id0 ASC, t.id1 ASC, t.hallnumber ASC, t0.id ASC, t0.id0 ASC, t1.ReservedSeancesID ASC, t1.ReservedSeatsID ASC, t1.id ASC, t2.BoughtSeancesID ASC, t2.BoughtSeatsID ASC),

          False, 
          False, 
          True
      )

      FROM (
          SELECT s.id, s.cinemahall_id, s.cost, s.film_id, s.seancedate, f.id AS id0, f.datefinish, f.datestart, f.description, f.duration, f.genre_id, f.title, f.poster, f.restriction, g.id AS id1, g.description AS description0, g.title AS title0, c.hallnumber, c.hallname

          INNER JOIN genre AS g ON f.genre_id = g.id
          INNER JOIN cinemahall AS c ON s.cinemahall_id = c.hallnumber
          WHERE s.id = @__id_0
          LIMIT 1
      ) AS t
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT h.id, h.cinemahall_id, h.row_number, h0.id AS id0, h0.hallrow_id, h0.seat_number
          FROM hallrow AS h

      Executing DbCommand [Parameters=[@__id_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
      SELECT s.id, s.cinemahall_id, s.cost, s.film_id, s.seancedate, f.id, f.datefinish, f.datestart, f.description, f.duration, f.genre_id, f.title, f.poster, f.restriction, g.id, g.description, g.title, c.hallnumber, c.hallname, t.id, t.cinemahall_id, t.row_number, t.id0, t.hallrow_id, t.seat_number
      FROM seance AS s
      INNER JOIN film AS f ON s.film_id = f.id
      INNER JOIN genre AS g ON f.genre_id = g.id
      INNER JOIN cinemahall AS c ON s.cinemahall_id = c.hallnumber
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT h.id, h.cinemahall_id, h.row_number, h0.id AS id0, h0.hallrow_id, h0.seat_number
          FROM hallrow AS h
          LEFT JOIN hallseat AS h0 ON h.id = h0.hallrow_id
      ) AS t ON c.hallnumber = t.cinemahall_id
      WHERE f.id = @__id_0
      ORDER BY s.id, f.id, g.id, c.hallnumber, t.id

          SELECT s.id, s.cinemahall_id, s.cost, s.film_id, s.seancedate, f.id AS id0, f.datefinish, f.datestart, f.description, f.duration, f.genre_id, f.title, f.poster, f.restriction, g.id AS id1, g.description AS description0, g.title AS title0, c.hallnumber, c.hallname
          FROM seance AS s
          INNER JOIN film AS f ON s.film_id = f.id
          INNER JOIN genre AS g ON f.genre_id = g.id
          INNER JOIN cinemahall AS c ON s.cinemahall_id = c.hallnumber
          WHERE s.id = @__id_0
          LIMIT 1
      ) AS t

          SELECT h.id, h.cinemahall_id, h.row_number, h0.id AS id0, h0.hallrow_id, h0.seat_number
          FROM hallrow AS h
          LEFT JOIN hallseat AS h0 ON h.id = h0.hallrow_id
      ) AS t0 ON t.hallnumber = t0.cinemahall_id
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT s0."ReservedSeancesID", s0."ReservedSeatsID", h1.id, h1.hallrow_id, h1.seat_number

      ) AS t1 ON t.id = t1."ReservedSeancesID"

                  FROM booking AS b
                  LEFT JOIN ticket AS t1 ON b.TicketID == t1.id
                  LEFT JOIN seance AS s ON t1.seance_id == s.id
                  LEFT JOIN film AS f ON s.film_id == f.id
                  LEFT JOIN genre AS g ON f.genre_id == g.id

                  LEFT JOIN hallrow AS h ON t1.row_id == h.id
                  LEFT JOIN hallseat AS h0 ON t1.seat_id == h0.id

          SELECT h.id, h.cinemahall_id, h.row_number, h0.id AS id0, h0.hallrow_id, h0.seat_number
          FROM hallrow AS h
          LEFT JOIN hallseat AS h0 ON h.id = h0.hallrow_id
      ) AS t ON c.hallnumber = t.cinemahall_id
      WHERE f.id = @__id_0
      ORDER BY s.id, f.id, g.id, c.hallnumber, t.id

              SELECT t.id, t.cinemahall_id, t.cost, t.film_id, t.seancedate, t.id0, t.datefinish, t.datestart, t.description, t.duration, t.genre_id, t.title, t.poster, t.restriction, t.id1, t.description0, t.title0, t.hallnumber, t.hallname, t0.id, t0.cinemahall_id, t0.row_number, t0.id0, t0.hallrow_id, t0.seat_number, t1.ReservedSeancesID, t1.ReservedSeatsID, t1.id, t1.hallrow_id, t1.seat_number, t2.BoughtSeancesID, t2.BoughtSeatsID, t2.id, t2.hallrow_id, t2.seat_number
              FROM 
              (
                  SELECT TOP(1) s.id, s.cinemahall_id, s.cost, s.film_id, s.seancedate, f.id AS id0, f.datefinish, f.datestart, f.description, f.duration, f.genre_id, f.title, f.poster, f.restriction, g.id AS id1, g.description AS description0, g.title AS title0, c.hallnumber, c.hallname
                  FROM seance AS s
                  INNER JOIN film AS f ON s.film_id == f.id
                  INNER JOIN genre AS g ON f.genre_id == g.id
                  INNER JOIN cinemahall AS c ON s.cinemahall_id == c.hallnumber
                  WHERE s.id == @__id_0
              ) AS t
              LEFT JOIN 
              (
                  SELECT h.id, h.cinemahall_id, h.row_number, h0.id AS id0, h0.hallrow_id, h0.seat_number
                  FROM hallrow AS h
                  LEFT JOIN hallseat AS h0 ON h.id == h0.hallrow_id
              ) AS t0 ON t.hallnumber == t0.cinemahall_id
              LEFT JOIN 
              (
                  SELECT s0.ReservedSeancesID, s0.ReservedSeatsID, h1.id, h1.hallrow_id, h1.seat_number
                  FROM SeanceReservedSeats AS s0
                  INNER JOIN hallseat AS h1 ON s0.ReservedSeatsID == h1.id
              ) AS t1 ON t.id == t1.ReservedSeancesID
              LEFT JOIN 
              (
                  SELECT s1.BoughtSeancesID, s1.BoughtSeatsID, h2.id, h2.hallrow_id, h2.seat_number
                  FROM SeanceBoughtSeats AS s1
                  INNER JOIN hallseat AS h2 ON s1.BoughtSeatsID == h2.id
              ) AS t2 ON t.id == t2.BoughtSeancesID
              ORDER BY t.id ASC, t.id0 ASC, t.id1 ASC, t.hallnumber ASC, t0.id ASC, t0.id0 ASC, t1.ReservedSeancesID ASC, t1.ReservedSeatsID ASC, t1.id ASC, t2.BoughtSeancesID ASC, t2.BoughtSeatsID ASC),

          CinemaLibrary.ApplicationContext, 
          False, 
          False, 
          True
      )
          .SingleOrDefault()'

      FROM (
          SELECT s.id, s.cinemahall_id, s.cost, s.film_id, s.seancedate, f.id AS id0, f.datefinish, f.datestart, f.description, f.duration, f.genre_id, f.title, f.poster, f.restriction, g.id AS id1, g.description AS description0, g.title AS title0, c.hallnumber, c.hallname
          FROM seance AS s
          INNER JOIN film AS f ON s.film_id = f.id
          INNER JOIN genre AS g ON f.genre_id = g.id
          INNER JOIN cinemahall AS c ON s.cinemahall_id = c.hallnumber
          WHERE s.id = @__id_0
          LIMIT 1
      ) AS t
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT h.id, h.cinemahall_id, h.row_number, h0.id AS id0, h0.hallrow_id, h0.seat_number
          FROM hallrow AS h
          LEFT JOIN hallseat AS h0 ON h.id = h0.hallrow_id
      ) AS t0 ON t.hallnumber = t0.cinemahall_id
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT s0."ReservedSeancesID", s0."ReservedSeatsID", h1.id, h1.hallrow_id, h1.seat_number
          FROM "SeanceReservedSeats" AS s0
          INNER JOIN hallseat AS h1 ON s0."ReservedSeatsID" = h1.id
      ) AS t1 ON t.id = t1."ReservedSeancesID"
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT s1."BoughtSeancesID", s1."BoughtSeatsID", h2.id, h2.hallrow_id, h2.seat_number
          FROM "SeanceBoughtSeats" AS s1
          INNER JOIN hallseat AS h2 ON s1."BoughtSeatsID" = h2.id
      ) AS t2 ON t.id = t2."BoughtSeancesID"
      ORDER BY t.id, t.id0, t.id1, t.hallnumber, t0.id, t0.id0, t1."ReservedSeancesID", t1."ReservedSeatsID", t1.id, t2."BoughtSeancesID", t2."BoughtSeatsID"

          SELECT s.id, s.cinemahall_id, s.cost, s.film_id, s.seancedate, f.id AS id0, f.datefinish, f.datestart, f.description, f.duration, f.genre_id, f.title, f.poster, f.restriction, g.id AS id1, g.description AS description0, g.title AS title0, c.hallnumber, c.hallname
          FROM seance AS s
          INNER JOIN film AS f ON s.film_id = f.id
          INNER JOIN genre AS g ON f.genre_id = g.id
          INNER JOIN cinemahall AS c ON s.cinemahall_id = c.hallnumber
          WHERE s.id = @__id_0
          LIMIT 1
      ) AS t
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT h.id, h.cinemahall_id, h.row_number, h0.id AS id0, h0.hallrow_id, h0.seat_number
          FROM hallrow AS h
          LEFT JOIN hallseat AS h0 ON h.id = h0.hallrow_id
      ) AS t0 ON t.hallnumber = t0.cinemahall_id
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT s0."ReservedSeancesID", s0."ReservedSeatsID", h1.id, h1.hallrow_id, h1.seat_number

          INNER JOIN hallseat AS h1 ON s0."ReservedSeatsID" = h1.id
      ) AS t1 ON t.id = t1."ReservedSeancesID"
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT s1."BoughtSeancesID", s1."BoughtSeatsID", h2.id, h2.hallrow_id, h2.seat_number
          FROM "SeanceBoughtSeats" AS s1

              SELECT t.id, t.cinemahall_id, t.cost, t.film_id, t.seancedate, t.id0, t.datefinish, t.datestart, t.description, t.duration, t.genre_id, t.title, t.poster, t.restriction, t.id1, t.description0, t.title0, t.hallnumber, t.hallname, t0.id, t0.cinemahall_id, t0.row_number, t0.id0, t0.hallrow_id, t0.seat_number, t1.ReservedSeancesID, t1.ReservedSeatsID, t1.id, t1.hallrow_id, t1.seat_number, t2.BoughtSeancesID, t2.BoughtSeatsID, t2.id, t2.hallrow_id, t2.seat_number
              FROM 
              (
                  SELECT TOP(1) s.id, s.cinemahall_id, s.cost, s.film_id, s.seancedate, f.id AS id0, f.datefinish, f.datestart, f.description, f.duration, f.genre_id, f.title, f.poster, f.restriction, g.id AS id1, g.description AS description0, g.title AS title0, c.hallnumber, c.hallname
                  FROM seance AS s
                  INNER JOIN film AS f ON s.film_id == f.id
                  INNER JOIN genre AS g ON f.genre_id == g.id
                  INNER JOIN cinemahall AS c ON s.cinemahall_id == c.hallnumber
                  WHERE s.id == @__id_0
              ) AS t
              LEFT JOIN 
              (
                  SELECT h.id, h.cinemahall_id, h.row_number, h0.id AS id0, h0.hallrow_id, h0.seat_number
                  FROM hallrow AS h
                  LEFT JOIN hallseat AS h0 ON h.id == h0.hallrow_id
              ) AS t0 ON t.hallnumber == t0.cinemahall_id
              LEFT JOIN 
              (
                  SELECT s0.ReservedSeancesID, s0.ReservedSeatsID, h1.id, h1.hallrow_id, h1.seat_number
                  FROM SeanceReservedSeats AS s0
                  INNER JOIN hallseat AS h1 ON s0.ReservedSeatsID == h1.id
              ) AS t1 ON t.id == t1.ReservedSeancesID
              LEFT JOIN 
              (
                  SELECT s1.BoughtSeancesID, s1.BoughtSeatsID, h2.id, h2.hallrow_id, h2.seat_number
                  FROM SeanceBoughtSeats AS s1
                  INNER JOIN hallseat AS h2 ON s1.BoughtSeatsID == h2.id
              ) AS t2 ON t.id == t2.BoughtSeancesID
              ORDER BY t.id ASC, t.id0 ASC, t.id1 ASC, t.hallnumber ASC, t0.id ASC, t0.id0 ASC, t1.ReservedSeancesID ASC, t1.ReservedSeatsID ASC, t1.id ASC, t2.BoughtSeancesID ASC, t2.BoughtSeatsID ASC),

          CinemaLibrary.ApplicationContext, 
          False, 
          False, 
          True
      )
          .SingleOrDefault()'

dbug: 25.06.2022 08:21:50.550 RelationalEventId.CommandExecuting[20100] (Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command) 
      Executing DbCommand [Parameters=[@__id_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
      SELECT t.id, t.cinemahall_id, t.cost, t.film_id, t.seancedate, t.id0, t.datefinish, t.datestart, t.description, t.duration, t.genre_id, t.title, t.poster, t.restriction, t.id1, t.description0, t.title0, t.hallnumber, t.hallname, t0.id, t0.cinemahall_id, t0.row_number, t0.id0, t0.hallrow_id, t0.seat_number, t1."ReservedSeancesID", t1."ReservedSeatsID", t1.id, t1.hallrow_id, t1.seat_number, t2."BoughtSeancesID", t2."BoughtSeatsID", t2.id, t2.hallrow_id, t2.seat_number
      FROM (
          SELECT s.id, s.cinemahall_id, s.cost, s.film_id, s.seancedate, f.id AS id0, f.datefinish, f.datestart, f.description, f.duration, f.genre_id, f.title, f.poster, f.restriction, g.id AS id1, g.description AS description0, g.title AS title0, c.hallnumber, c.hallname
          FROM seance AS s
          INNER JOIN film AS f ON s.film_id = f.id
          INNER JOIN genre AS g ON f.genre_id = g.id
          INNER JOIN cinemahall AS c ON s.cinemahall_id = c.hallnumber
          WHERE s.id = @__id_0
          LIMIT 1
      ) AS t
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT h.id, h.cinemahall_id, h.row_number, h0.id AS id0, h0.hallrow_id, h0.seat_number
          FROM hallrow AS h
          LEFT JOIN hallseat AS h0 ON h.id = h0.hallrow_id
      ) AS t0 ON t.hallnumber = t0.cinemahall_id
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT s0."ReservedSeancesID", s0."ReservedSeatsID", h1.id, h1.hallrow_id, h1.seat_number
          FROM "SeanceReservedSeats" AS s0
          INNER JOIN hallseat AS h1 ON s0."ReservedSeatsID" = h1.id
      ) AS t1 ON t.id = t1."ReservedSeancesID"
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT s1."BoughtSeancesID", s1."BoughtSeatsID", h2.id, h2.hallrow_id, h2.seat_number
          FROM "SeanceBoughtSeats" AS s1
          INNER JOIN hallseat AS h2 ON s1."BoughtSeatsID" = h2.id
      ) AS t2 ON t.id = t2."BoughtSeancesID"
      ORDER BY t.id, t.id0, t.id1, t.hallnumber, t0.id, t0.id0, t1."ReservedSeancesID", t1."ReservedSeatsID", t1.id, t2."BoughtSeancesID", t2."BoughtSeatsID"
info: 25.06.2022 08:21:50.579 RelationalEventId.CommandExecuted[20101] (Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command) 
      Executed DbCommand (28ms) [Parameters=[@__id_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
      SELECT t.id, t.cinemahall_id, t.cost, t.film_id, t.seancedate, t.id0, t.datefinish, t.datestart, t.description, t.duration, t.genre_id, t.title, t.poster, t.restriction, t.id1, t.description0, t.title0, t.hallnumber, t.hallname, t0.id, t0.cinemahall_id, t0.row_number, t0.id0, t0.hallrow_id, t0.seat_number, t1."ReservedSeancesID", t1."ReservedSeatsID", t1.id, t1.hallrow_id, t1.seat_number, t2."BoughtSeancesID", t2."BoughtSeatsID", t2.id, t2.hallrow_id, t2.seat_number
      FROM (
          SELECT s.id, s.cinemahall_id, s.cost, s.film_id, s.seancedate, f.id AS id0, f.datefinish, f.datestart, f.description, f.duration, f.genre_id, f.title, f.poster, f.restriction, g.id AS id1, g.description AS description0, g.title AS title0, c.hallnumber, c.hallname
          FROM seance AS s
          INNER JOIN film AS f ON s.film_id = f.id
          INNER JOIN genre AS g ON f.genre_id = g.id
          INNER JOIN cinemahall AS c ON s.cinemahall_id = c.hallnumber
          WHERE s.id = @__id_0
          LIMIT 1
      ) AS t
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT h.id, h.cinemahall_id, h.row_number, h0.id AS id0, h0.hallrow_id, h0.seat_number
          FROM hallrow AS h
          LEFT JOIN hallseat AS h0 ON h.id = h0.hallrow_id
      ) AS t0 ON t.hallnumber = t0.cinemahall_id
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT s0."ReservedSeancesID", s0."ReservedSeatsID", h1.id, h1.hallrow_id, h1.seat_number
          FROM "SeanceReservedSeats" AS s0
          INNER JOIN hallseat AS h1 ON s0."ReservedSeatsID" = h1.id
      ) AS t1 ON t.id = t1."ReservedSeancesID"
      LEFT JOIN (
          SELECT s1."BoughtSeancesID", s1."BoughtSeatsID", h2.id, h2.hallrow_id, h2.seat_number
          FROM "SeanceBoughtSeats" AS s1
          INNER JOIN hallseat AS h2 ON s1."BoughtSeatsID" = h2.id
      ) AS t2 ON t.id = t2."BoughtSeancesID"
      ORDER BY t.id, t.id0, t.id1, t.hallnumber, t0.id, t0.id0, t1."ReservedSeancesID", t1."ReservedSeatsID", t1.id, t2."BoughtSeancesID", t2."BoughtSeatsID"
